A range of luxury one and two bedroom apartments with parking

Location

Oxford offers a wealth of amenities and the location of the apartments gives easy access to both the centre of Oxford via bus from Thornhill Park and Ride next door and to London via the Oxford Tube.

For those driving its proximity to the A40 and junction 8 of the M40 makes it extremely accessible to London and the north, and there is a regular train service from Oxford Parkway to London Marylebone.

A selection of shops are within walking distance including a local convenience store and pharmacy, larger facilities can be found in Headington approx. 5 minutes via car and 7 minutes cycling, again direct buses available from the Park & Ride, including restaurants, shops and a Waitrose.

The centre of Oxford, approx. 3.5 miles away, offers a wide range of shops and the recently built Westgate shopping cente with roof top bars and restaurants and a Curzon cinema.

There are many green open spaces in Oxford but the closest is Shotover Country Park, an area of outstanding natural beauty and a protected nature reserve extending to some 300 acres of woodlands, fields and valleys. The Park is accessible to the public for riding, walking and general recreation.

Description

Savills are delighted to offer a selection of luxury apartments Thornhill Park, Oxford. Apartments are spread over three floors, two lifts service the block, in a leafy location set back from London Road. There are a range of apartments available over the coming months at different prices.

The apartments have been finished to a very high standard with quality fixtures and fittings, the kitchens include built in tall fridge / freezer, built in dishwasher, oven and electric hob. All flats have a separate utility cupboard with a washer / dryer. The open plan kitchen / living rooms have high ceilings with most apartments benefiting from floor to ceiling, double glazed, widows providing ample natural light.

The fully tiled bathrooms have a vanity cabinet, shower over bath and a large porcelain sink with mixer tap. There is a large landscaped communal garden in the centre of the building for tenants to enjoy and all tenants benefit from one parking space included with additional parking available by separate negotiation, there is also a communal bicycle storage room in the basement of the building.

Entrance to the building is via a fob entry system and all apartments have a video entry phone system.
